an/4502270.bio">Ben Flatman</a></span></p><p class="intro">The shadow levelling-up secretary has taken flak for exercising her right to buy, but Labour has a long history of dalliance with the concept of selling council homes, writes Ben Flatman</p></div></li><li><p class="picture"><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/opinion/similar-but-not-the-same-how-qualifying-as-an-architect-differs-between-the-us-and-uk/5128944.article" class="image"><img alt="Chris Fogarty Headshot_cropped" class="lazyloaded" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 50vw, (max-width: 768px) 10vw, (max-width: 1024px) 15vw, (max-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1281px) 21vw, 100vw" src="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/4/3/5/1975435_chrisfogartyheadshot_cropped_279434_crop.jpg" srcset="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/4/3/5/1975435_chrisfogartyheadshot_cropped_279434_crop.jpg 415w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/230x153/4/3/5/1975435_chrisfogartyheadshot_cropped_279434_crop.jpg 230w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/320x213/4/3/5/1975435_chrisfogartyheadshot_cropped_279434_crop.jpg 320w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/375x250/4/3/5/1975435_chrisfogartyheadshot_cropped_279434_crop.jpg 375w" width="415" height="277" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/opinion/similar-but-not-the-same-how-qualifying-as-an-architect-differs-between-the-us-and-uk/5128944.article">Similar, but not the same: How qualifying as an architect differs between the US and UK</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="date" data-date-timezone="{&quot;publishdate&quot;: &quot;2024-04-17T05:00:00&quot;}">2024-04-17T05:00:00+01:00</span><span class="author">By <a rel="author" href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/chris-fogarty/4503654.bio">Chris Fogarty</a></span><span class="commentCount"><span class="count">1</span><span class="assistive"> comments</span></span></p><p class="intro">When Chris Fogarty’s daughter expr