op.jpg 375w" width="415" height="277" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/opinion/what-the-second-staircase-guidance-means-for-the-industry/5128689.article">What the second staircase guidance means for the industry</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="date" data-date-timezone="{&quot;publishdate&quot;: &quot;2024-04-02T09:12:00&quot;}">2024-04-02T09:12:00+01:00</span><span class="author">By <span class="noLink">Andrew Mellor</span></span></p><p class="intro">The long-awaited guidance will give developers confidence to proceed on projects, but debates will continue, writes Andrew Mellor</p></div></li><li><p class="picture"><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/news/his-legacy-will-stand-for-generations-chris-dyson-pays-tribute-to-artist-richard-serra/5128676.article" class="image"><img alt="shutterstock_1932738953" class="lazyloaded" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 50vw, (max-width: 768px) 10vw, (max-width: 1024px) 15vw, (max-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1281px) 21vw, 100vw" src="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/3/6/5/1974365_shutterstock_1932738953_219498.jpg" srcset="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/3/6/5/1974365_shutterstock_1932738953_219498.jpg 415w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/230x153/3/6/5/1974365_shutterstock_1932738953_219498.jpg 230w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/320x213/3/6/5/1974365_shutterstock_1932738953_219498.jpg 320w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/375x250/3/6/5/1974365_shutterstock_1932738953_219498.jpg 375w" width="415" height="277" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/news/his-legacy-will-stand-for-generations-chris-dyson-pays-tribute-to-artist-richard-serra/5128676.article">‘His legacy will stand for generations’: Chris Dyson pays tribute to artist Richard Serra</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="date" data-date-timezone="{&quot;publishdate&quot;: &quot;2024-03-28T13:18:00&quot;}">2024-03-28T13:18:00+00:00</span><span class="author">By <a rel="author" href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/chris-dyson/4503098.bio">Chris Dyson</a></span></p><p class="intro">The Chris Dyson Architects founder describes how he has been influenced by the American abstract artist, who died this week at the age of 85</p></div></li><li><p class="picture"><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/opinion/even-a-shopping-centre-can-have-emotional-resonance-and-that-value-is-hard-to-quantify/5128515.article" class="image"><img alt="Martyn Evans index" class="lazyloaded" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 50vw, (max-width: 768px) 10vw, (max-width: 1024px) 15vw, (max-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1281px) 21vw, 100vw" src="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/7/2/5/1973725_Martyn-Evans-index.jpg" srcset="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/7/2/5/1973725_Martyn-Evans-index.jpg 415w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/230x153/7/2/5/1973725_Martyn-Evans-index.jpg 230w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/320x213/7/2/5/1973725_Martyn-Evans-index.jpg 320w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/375x250/7/2/5/1973725_Martyn-Evans-index.jpg 375w" width="415" height="277" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/opinion/even-a-shopping-centre-can-have-emotional-resonance-and-that-value-is-hard-to-quantify/5128515.article">Even a shopping centre can have emotional resonance - and that value is hard to quantify</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="date" data-date-timezone="{&quot;publishdate&quot;: &quot;2024-03-27T00:05:00&quot;}">2024-03-27T00:05:00+00:00</span><span class="author">By <a rel="author" href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/martyn-evans/4502292.bio">Martyn Evans</a></span><span class="commentCount"><span class="count">2</span><span class="assistive"> comments</span></span></p><p class="intro">When visitors start scattering their loved ones’ ashes, you know you’ve developed a precious connection to place, writes Martyn Evans</p></div></li><li><p class="picture"><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/buildings-design-and-specification/a-call-for-regulation-maximising-fire-safety-through-intumescent-application/5128528.article" class="image"><img alt="intumescent paint sprayer on steel shutterstock" class="lazyloaded" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 50vw, (max-width: 768px) 10vw, (max-width: 1024px) 15vw, (max-width: 1280px) 20vw, (min-width: 1281px) 21vw, 100vw" src="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/8/3/7/1973837_intumescentpaintsprayeronsteelshutterstock_618236_crop.jpg" srcset="https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/415x277/8/3/7/1973837_intumescentpaintsprayeronsteelshutterstock_618236_crop.jpg 415w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/230x153/8/3/7/1973837_intumescentpaintsprayeronsteelshutterstock_618236_crop.jpg 230w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/320x213/8/3/7/1973837_intumescentpaintsprayeronsteelshutterstock_618236_crop.jpg 320w,https://d3rcx32iafnn0o.cloudfront.net/Pictures/375x250/8/3/7/1973837_intumescentpaintsprayeronsteelshutterstock_618236_crop.jpg 375w" width="415" height="277" /></a></p><div class="subSleeve"><h2><a href="https://www.bdonline.co.uk/buildings-design-and-specification/a-call-for-regulation-maximising-fire-safety-through-intumescent-application/5128528.article">A call for regulation: Maximising fire safety through intumescent application</a></h2><p class="meta"><span class="date" data-date-timezone="{&quot;publishdate&quot;: &quot;2024-03-26T05:00:00&quot;}">2024-03-26T05:00:00+00:00</span><span class="author">By <span class="noLink">Jo Thornicroft</span></span></p><p class="intro">Despite positive steps for safety in the built environment, crucial areas are still being overlooked. Jo Thornicroft explores the role of intumescent paint in fire safety and why a regulatory body is needed</p></div></li><li><p class="picture"><a href="https://